node.title: Late Night Celebrates Biden’s 79th Birthday
node.alt: Jimmy Fallon, who noted that President Biden spent his birthday going to 5 o’clock Mass, said, “Man, does this guy know how to party or what?”
node.description: Jimmy Fallon joked that when the president blew out his candles, “everyone started clapping and the lights went on and off.”
node.content: ["Welcome to Best of Late Night, a rundown of the previous night\u2019s highlights that lets you sleep \u2014 and lets us get paid to watch comedy. Here are the 50 best movies on Netflix right now.", "Late Night belatedly celebrated President Biden\u2019s 79th birthday, which took place over the weekend.", "\u201cBiden spent his birthday in Wilmington, Delaware, and went to a 5 o\u2019clock Mass. Man, does this guy know how to party or what?\u201d Jimmy Fallon said on Monday night. \u201cI mean, even Mike Pence was like, \u2018Ever heard of Chuck E.
